{"tid":1532204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔何郭佩珍中學事件簡單整合","createTime":"2019-09-02T12:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:23:17.000Z","uid":193209,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8854087d91b644f467b00fa8f553e9bdad70fea7","tid":1532204,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:48:36.000Z","msg":"好似無乜人知發生咩事，做個簡單整合<br />\n利申聽樓下保安個女個三姑媽個朋友講<br />\n今朝狂抽人條八婆話要交罷課名單比教育局<br />\n條片流出後好多人去聲援（其實開頭係學生多）<br />\n咁啱同時何中隔離層樓有手足企跳（層樓同學校係只有幾步之隔）<br />\n果時好撚大雨，聲援手足聲淚俱下大叫唔好跳，齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個畫面係文字形容唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後手足被救（聽說係尋晚尋死果位手足）<br />\n大家高興完同道謝消防後就將目光放返入學校事件到<br />\n之後學校搵咗副校出嚟，話想同大家對話解決，大家唔收貨<br />\n叫狂抽人條八婆直接出嚟同大家對話<br />\n當然條八婆唔會出嚟<br />\n搞咗一輸有舊生入去同佢地對話<br />\n（大埔group好似有live，我去咗食嘢唔肯定）<br />\n然後有條友話自己係唔知咩其他學校家長校董會之類出來講嘢<br />\n講講吓嘢狂抽人條八婆想渣車走<br />\n咁大家就去圍佢唔比佢走<br />\n狂抽人想比油，佢踩油咗一吓無撞到人<br />\n呢個時候果條咩學校家長校董會條友叫大家比佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足們當然無理條左膠，狂抽人就縮返入學校<br />\n之後樓下保安個女個三姑媽個朋友有嘢做就走先<br />\n而家手足們無圍學校，但成條邨都聽到手足們嗌緊口號<br />\n我聽返嚟就係到呢到，後續大家有消息希望大家補充"},{"pid":"28582c7d5be80e4c80d2bf723795888ab164672b","tid":1532204,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"我想問下大埔仲有無tg group<br />\n去緊接放學"},{"pid":"f35b996e1b2b8cec78dd6e9421c4a01c7c01f087","tid":1532204,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"【召集】所有住近學校嘅巴絲打聽朝係學校早會時大叫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532161</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法聲援佢地點睇？<br />\n難d拉人"},{"pid":"5a6c14470e296296d3a9552d4ada2e78309b8df9","tid":1532204,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e72e2d9a6368ed410f32a1a2c325d0b5b4a895b9","tid":1532204,"uid":315924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:54:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推到江永祥仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n仲有幾個鐘就返學啦好緊張<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"015c01ad6de1b197f84596cf5e4eaf178d0c6541","tid":1532204,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28582c7d5be80e4c80d2bf723795888ab164672b","tid":1532204,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"我想問下大埔仲有無tg group<br />\n去緊接放學"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"Sor巴打我都唔知<br />\n而家突然靜晒<br />\n我都想知咩事"},{"pid":"5205b48a7359f165198bd6a003bb407ba6093756","tid":1532204,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:59:30.000Z","msg":"[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪 [國難老闆同一眾員工已保釋,開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff6e78854c77ccadbca1ff34799ea55e95729db","tid":1532204,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"015c01ad6de1b197f84596cf5e4eaf178d0c6541","tid":1532204,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dis